I have duely recd. yd of 9 & 21. cortt., as for the valeutation of the resting goods
1682 p Jan. I have noted accordingly, Intrim I hope you have sold those
remainders, if not all, att least that you will do mee good for them to cleare that
& to make mij share yd owne, of which att yd leafure defre yd answer. as for
the faising mills, I seawe not one word yet, butt as soone as they come, you shall
heare off itt, & I shall follow, yd diratons, whilst you will do well to delay the
wonen with faure words, or satiigye, with good deeds yd self of they deserve it
